{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4dd6d892fc","title":"在中央机关抽调万名干部下放基层情况报告上的批语","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"44fb9327bb","index":0,"year":1960,"month":11,"day":15,"articleId":"4dd6d892fc"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"64a9ed364e","type":"title","text":"在中央机关抽调万名干部下放基层情况报告上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"4dd6d892fc"},{"id":"98655e9aed","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"4dd6d892fc"},{"id":"a52b4f0b00","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"4dd6d892fc"},{"id":"b4a19f2bd4","type":"appellation","text":"总理：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"4dd6d892fc"},{"id":"23a6894bd7","type":"paragraph","text":"在讲大好形势、学习政策的过程中，要有一段时间大讲三分之一地区的不好形势，坏人当权，打人死人，粮食减产，吃不饱饭，民主革命尚未完成，封建势力大大作怪，对社会主义更加仇视，破坏社会主义的生产关系和生产力，农村工作极为艰苦，要有坚强意志决不怕苦的精神才能去，否则不能去。以上请你酌定。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"4dd6d892fc"},{"id":"7e306f6270","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东十五日晨","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"4dd6d892fc"},{"id":"83f99a3301","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"4dd6d892fc"},{"id":"5c5d6cd917","type":"paragraph","text":"全国大好形势，占三分之二地区；又有大不好形势，占三分之一的地区。五个月内，一定要把全部形势都转变过来。共产党要有这样一种本领，五个月工作的转变，一定争取1961年的农业大丰收，一切坏人坏事都改过来，邪气下降，正气上升。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"4dd6d892fc"}],"page":{"id":"64056f85e8","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"4dd6d892fc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}